@startuml
title State diagram of the system operations of "Safehome Security Function"

[*] --> PowerOnCheck

state "Power-On Check" as PowerOnCheck
state "System Stopped" as SystemStopped
state "System Ready" as SystemReady
state "Monitoring" as Monitoring
state "Alarm Activated" as AlarmActivated
state "False Alarm" as FalseAlarm
state "Password Entered" as PasswordEntered

PowerOnCheck --> SystemStopped : problem detected
PowerOnCheck --> SystemReady : no problem detected
SystemReady --> SystemReady : reset
SystemReady --> SystemReady : activate
SystemReady --> SystemReady : turn off
SystemReady --> Monitoring : activate
Monitoring --> Monitoring : continue monitoring
Monitoring --> AlarmActivated : sensor triggered
AlarmActivated --> SystemReady : false alarm or time ends
SystemReady --> PasswordEntered : password entered

@enduml
